metadata.name: Broken Dreams
metadata.description:
Self portrait of me back in 13 years old , where my parents did not see a vision for me creating arts . They took away my favourite sketch book , so I couldn't draw . Feeling like my dreams were broken . 

Now I'm 17 , creating arts for you . You might know me on Opensea , now I have a trading volume of 0.88 eth . Have a wonderful day , dear readers .
